                "invention-title": [
                    "Cement clinker low-carbon production method and system for carbonate hydrogenation in-situ catalytic reduction",
                    "碳酸盐加氢原位催化还原的水泥熟料低碳生产方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a cement clinker low-carbon production method and system for carbonate hydrogenation in-situ catalytic reduction, and the system comprises a rotary kiln, a smoke chamber, a combustion furnace, a first reactor for CO2 carbonation, a first cyclone cylinder, a second reactor for carbonate decomposition, a second cyclone cylinder, a third cyclone cylinder for preheating, a gas separation device and a gas-solid combustor, cO2 in the fuel is carbonated into carbonate through circulation of metal oxide, the carbonate and the carbonate preheated by cyclone in the raw materials are hydrogenated together and subjected to an in-situ catalytic reduction reaction under the action of a catalyst, and the obtained high-temperature hydrogen-containing coal gas can be used for providing heat for a kiln system. According to the invention, C which is originally converted into CO2 in fuel and raw materials is subjected to in-situ catalytic reduction into hydrogen-containing coal gas, and the hydrogen-containing coal gas and pulverized coal/biomass alternative fuel are mixed and combusted to realize kiln calorific value replacement, so that not only is carbon dioxide emission in the whole production process of cement clinker reduced, but also NOX emission in flue gas in a kiln can be improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种碳酸盐加氢原位催化还原的水泥熟料低碳生产方法及系统，包括回转窑、烟室、燃烧炉、用于CO2碳酸化的第一反应器、第一旋风筒、用于碳酸盐分解的第二反应器、第二旋风筒、用于预热的第三旋风筒、气体分离装置和气固燃烧器，利用金属氧化物的循环，将燃料中的CO2碳酸化为碳酸盐，连同原料中旋风预热后的碳酸盐一同加氢在催化剂作用下进行原位催化还原反应，得到的高温含氢煤气可用于为窑炉系统提供热量。本发明将燃料及原料中本来会转化为CO2的C，原位催化还原为含氢煤气,并与煤粉/生物质替代燃料掺混燃烧实现窑炉热值替代，不仅减少了水泥熟料生产全过程中的二氧化碳排放，而且还可以改善窑炉中烟气中NOX的排放。"
                }
            ]
